</div>
</div>
</div>
<div></div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13073644/ni4a6032-1.jpg" alt="Aurora Cabins" data-udi="umb://media/43e1b2719817440ab42237c4465b8a4a" />
<h2>Aurora Cabins, Levi and Saariselkä</h2>
<p>With two separate sites with little light pollution, the Aurora Cabins are available for both Levi and Saariselka guests to enjoy. Northern Lights Village is located 17km from Levi and the Saariselka site is 10 minutes walk from the centre. A magical way to experience the wintry star-filled sky and dancing Northern Lights, with the laser-heated glass roof located directly above the king size bed, giving you a perfect view of the night sky. </p>
<p><strong>Aurora Cabins, sleep 1-4. </strong><span>A continental breakfast is included in our prices and an optional dinner at the cabin location's restaurant may be pre-booked. All cabins include sofa bed, private en suite with shower room, fridge, kettle and free Wi-Fi. (Maximum 3 adults, or 2 adults and 1-2 children).</span><span class="listelem_value"></span></p>
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><a href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi" class="c-btn">Holidays to Levi</a></td>
<td> </td>
<td><a href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka" class="c-btn">Holidays to Saariselka</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>Please Note:</strong></p>
<p>We act as at all times as the selling agent for the supplier of excursions and activities.</p>
<p>These overnight stays can be pre-booked but the exact day of the week will be confirmed once booked, as all reservations are subject to availability. </p>
<p>Child ages for the Aurora Cabins are 4 - 14 years. The Golden Crown Igloos are 4 - 12 years. Children aged 0 - 3 years are free if sharing the main bed with the adults. </p>
</div>
