  <shortDescription><![CDATA[<p>Glass igloos are unique to Lapland. Unlike anywhere else in the world, it is difficult to fully enjoy the beauty and majesty of the untouched Arctic Circle in Northern Finland at night due to the cold. We offer our guests the opportunity to stay in one of these igloos as an excursion for 1 night during their holiday to either Levi or Saariselkä.</p>]]></shortDescription>
